There will be following components:
a) Home : Will have Source  and Destination city name  and date , number of passengers and a search button. 
c) Flight Listing: Once that search button is clicked a list of flights matching that criterion will be displayed.   Each item in the list will have a book button. User should be able to go back the home page from here.
d)Booking:  Once   book button is clicked a final booking page will come where user will be able to key in passengers names and once submit button is clicked a PNR will be generated and  on the   screen and user will be send back to Home Page.
Optional Requirement : Upon completetion of the  booking a Receipt with all booking details like passengers name,PNR number,Source   and Destination airport and the total price of the ticket.
You may add any more components if required to fulfil these requirement
